    "description": {
      "value": "<p><b>Source</b> <em>Adventurer's Armory 2 pg. 9</em>, <em>Gnomes of Golarion pg. 22</em></p><h3><span title=\"PFS Legal\">[PFS]</span> Statistics</h3><p><b>Cost</b> 70 gp <b>Weight</b> 15 lbs.</p><p><b>Damage</b> 1d8 (small), 1d10 (medium); <b>Critical</b> x2; <b>Range</b> -; <b>Type</b> B; <b>Special</b> see text</p><p><b>Category</b> Two-Handed; <b>Proficiency</b> Exotic</p><p><b>Weapon Groups</b> Hammers</p><h3>Description</h3><p>An alchemically fired piston in the head of this two-handed hammer strikes targets with astounding force. Successful sunder attacks made with a piston maul deal an additional 4 points of damage. A piston maul requires a thunderstone to function; otherwise, it functions as a greatclub. Inserting a thunderstone into the weapon's compartment is a standard action, and powers the weapon for 24 hours, after which the thunderstone is consumed.</p>"
